Component: 
"building blocks" of react apps.

- Start with a capital, why? -> JSX can contain components
- a function that returns JSX.

////////////////////////////////////////

JSX:
syntax that mixes HTML in JS code.
use JS in JSW expression? -> use {}.

when writing HTML in JSX: 'class' becomes 'className'

